quran[28{c,v,t}:
69,35,Falaysa lahul yawma haahunaa hameem
69,36,Wa laa ta'aamun illaa min ghisleen
69,37,Laa yaakuluhooo illal khati'oon
69,38,Falaaa uqsimu bimaa tubsiroon
69,39,Wa maa laa tubsiroon
69,40,Innahoo laqawlu Rasoolin kareem
69,41,Wa ma huwa biqawli shaa'ir; qaleelam maa tu'minoon
69,42,Wa laa biqawli kaahin; qaleelam maa tazakkaroon
69,43,Tanzeelum mir rabbil 'aalameen
69,44,Wa law taqawwala 'alainaa ba'dal aqaaweel
69,45,La-akhaznaa minhu bilyameen
69,46,Summa laqata'naa minhul wateen
69,47,Famaa minkum min ahadin'anhu haajizeen
69,48,Wa innahoo latazkiratul lilmuttaqeen
69,49,Wa inna lana'lamu anna minkum mukazzibeen
69,50,Wa innahu lahasratun 'alal kaafireen
69,51,Wa innahoo lahaqqul yaqeen
69,52,Fasbbih bismi Rabbikal 'Azeem
70,1,Sa ala saaa'ilum bi'azaa binw-waaqi'
70,2,Lilkaafireen laisa lahoo daafi'
70,3,Minal laahi zil ma'aarij
70,4,Ta'rujul malaaa'ikatu war Roohu ilaihi fee yawmin kaana miqdaaruhoo khamseena alfa sanah
70,5,Fasbir ssabran jameelaa
70,6,Inaahum yarawnahoo ba'eedaa
70,7,Wa naraahu qareebaa
70,8,Yawma takoonus samaaa'u kalmuhl
70,9,Wa takoonul jibaalu kal'ihn
70,10,Wa laa yas'alu hameemun hameemaa
